Attributes.description: Human cognition, perception, motor, social, emotional needs, brain development and their interactions from birth until the emergence of language.
Attributes.prereq: Pre-reqs: Either (a) PSYC 100 or (b) two of PSYC 101, PSYC 102, PSYC 205, PSYC 207, PSYC 208, PSYC 216, PSYC 217, PSYC 277. (Strongly recommended: PSYC 101, 102, and PSYC 216 or one of PSYC 217 or 277.)
